{
  "id": "adv_bond_smr_01_05",
  "title": "奥山すみれ5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "うう、お腹空いた……でも今日は午後から食レポの\nロケがあるから我慢しないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ I'm so hungry… but I have to hold out\nfor the food report shoot later today…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？　くんくん……このいい匂いは……\nあー！　キッチンに芋煮が……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hm? Sniff‚ sniff… what’s this delicious smell?\nAh! There’s imoni in the kitchen…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.1666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、その隣のお鍋にはおしるこもあるっちゃ……！？\nでも、なんでこんな所に！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-And there's sweet red bean soup in the pot next to it too…!?\nBut why is it here?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.2666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！　私をお腹一杯にさせてロケを失敗\nさせようとした誰かが……！？　なんてあくどい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ha! Is someone trying to make me full so I'll\nfail the shoot…!? How wicked…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……ちょっとくらいなら大丈夫、だよね？\n味見するだけ、一口だけ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-But… a little bit shouldn't hurt‚ right?\nJust a taste‚ just one bite…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.5666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "ん～～～～！　美味しい～～！\n空腹の胃におしるこが染みるよ～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm~~~~! It's delicious~~~~!\nThe sweet bean soup is soothing my empty stomach~…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.7999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "芋煮も、一口だけ……あっ！\n里芋をおしるこの中に落としちゃった…",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just one bite of the imoni too… Oops!\nI dropped a taro root into the red bean soup…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5666659038,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3166.667429500002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　せっかくだし、お餅で芋を包んで……\nいただきまーす………………！　こ、これは……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know! Since it's already there‚ I'll wrap the taro in mochi…\nHere we go………! Th-This is…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "お、美味しい……！　甘味のあるお餅を噛むと\n芋煮の出汁が効いた里芋がじゅわっと現れる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-It’s so good…! When you bite into the sweet mochi‚\nthe savory taro soaked in broth just bursts out…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "これは世紀の大発明っちゃ……！\n食の常識が変わってしまうっちゃ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is the greatest invention of the century…!\nThis will change the world of food forever!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "今度お兄ちゃんに教えてあげよっと！\nそれにしても、美味しいなぁ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to tell my big brother about this later!\nIt’s so good‚ though~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.0333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、今の食レポもいい感じだったよね？\nこれでこの後のロケも絶好調だよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And my food report just now was pretty spot-on‚ right?\nI'll be in top form for the shoot later~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1000068665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、もう一個包んで……ぱくっ！\nん～～～～～！　これは本当に凄いっちゃ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ let’s wrap another one… Nom!\nMmm~~~~~! This is truly amazing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.1000068665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "あと一個だけなら大丈夫だよね？\nぱくっ……ん～～～～～！　ぱくっ！　ん～～～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just one more should be fine‚ right?\nNom… Mmm~~~~~! Nom! Mmm~~~~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.4666801454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "はっ……！？　お鍋に一粒の小豆もない！　気付いたら\n芋煮とおしるこ、全部食べてしまったっちゃ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…!? There’s not a single bean left! Before I knew it‚\nI ate all the imoni and red bean soup!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4666964215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしよう……誰のお鍋だったのかな……\nあー！　それよりこの後食レポが控えてるっちゃ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-What should I do… whose pots were those?…\nAh! More importantly‚ the shoot is starting soon…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.4666964215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "まずいっちゃまずいっちゃ、今からこの間テレビで見た\n『高速消化促進体操』でなんとか……！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm in trouble‚ I'm in trouble! I'll use that\n\"High-Speed Digestion Gymnastics\" to somehow…!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.8333630881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、いくぞ～！　いちに、さんっし！\nよんごで消化！　ごろくでゴロゴロ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ here we go~! One‚ two‚ three‚ four!\nDigestion on five and six! Rolling on seven and eight…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.8000297548,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10799.986521300014
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、沙季さん……！　すみません\n騒がしかったですよね……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Saki-san…! I’m so sorry.\nI was being too noisy‚ wasn't I?…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.5000297548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　夕食のために作り置きしていた\n芋煮とおしるこを知らないかって……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? You're asking if I've seen the imoni\nand red bean soup you prepped for dinner…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.4666964215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_05-smr021.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、その……今、消化中というか……なんというか\n……うわーん！　ごめんなさいっちゃ～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ um… you could say they're currently digesting…\n…Waaah! I’m so sorry!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.9333630881,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}